<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Digital Den Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f0f13;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #1e1e24;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #b19cd9;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .action-btn {
            background: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .logout {
            color: #e74c3c;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Dashboard</h1>
        <div class="user-info">
            <span>Logged in as <%= user.username %></span>
            <a href="/auth/logout" class="logout" style="margin-left: 15px;">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Server Status</h3>
            <p>🟢 Online</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Members</h3>
            <!-- In a real app, pass this data from the route by querying the bot client -->
            <p>Manage via Bot</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Actions</h3>
            <button class="action-btn" onclick="alert('Feature coming soon!')">Sync Roles</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <h2>Management Controls</h2>
        <p>Use the Discord client logic to manage real-time events. This dashboard can be expanded to show logs, member
            lists, etc.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>